PrecisAmendment to the BRITISH COLUMBIA SPORT FISHING REGULATIONS which reduces, from four to three, the possession limit on chinook salmon caught by sport fishing in the tidal waters off the west coast of Vancouver Island, effective July 17, 1995.

precis:
Amendment to the BRITISH COLUMBIA SPORT FISHING REGULATIONS which reduces,
from four to three, the possession limit on chinook salmon caught by sport
fishing in the tidal waters off the west coast of Vancouver Island,
effective July 17, 1995.
